19:["$","p","p-9",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Leuchtturm1917"}]," is the better notebook for desk use, daily journaling, planning, and anyone who uses fountain pens or fine gel pens. The page quality and organizational features make it worth the small price difference."]}]
1a:["$","p","p-10",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Moleskine"}]," wins if portability and aesthetics matter more than paper quality — or if you're buying for a gift and the recipient is brand-conscious."]}]
